Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.48,SFX-GrayWhite,Sign 0002,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12}{\an2}Raspberry Shortcake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:14.50,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,We have a new part-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.06,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she started today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:18.08,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,She says she loves our cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.42,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach her everything \Nyou know, Ichinose-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:23.20,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.93,Title1,Sign 0155,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,188)}My Spring Break
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:57.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:57.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:00.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You look way too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:01.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:06.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess being worried is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:11.52,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0209,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}That's a sudden epiphany there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:11.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to be ready, in case \Nanything happens to Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.90,SFX-Red,Sign 0216,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:20.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How was work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:26.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you encouraged me to apply, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:32.28,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I think their cakes are the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:32.92,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.08,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so intricate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:38.23,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how they're made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:40.68,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I want to see them all being made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.51,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0242,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}Help Wanted {\fs18}\N\NPâtissier \NPâtissier Assistant \NSales Staff \N\N(High school student and \Ntemp positions available) \N\NAsk staff for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.88,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:43.51,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.38,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.25,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:56.14,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but if I do, I might not be able \Nto spend as much time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.82,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally spring break, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.45,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Spring comes every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.78,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to try something \Nyou've always wanted to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.83,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So this cake is from Les Cerises.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of looks like it was constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like it's made of plastic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:16.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.05,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0319,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(570,1)\an9}I have no idea where to start eating it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's saying it's like a work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:20.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:21.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.77,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.56,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So, like Yamato said, this is a professional's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Digging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.56,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0330,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:40.07,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I say something \Nmore insightful, damn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes kind of complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:51.08,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0345,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Good job, Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:51.08,SFX-GrayWhite,Sign 0345,0000,0000,0000,,It's tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's rich, but not too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:51.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The way they use liquor is innovative, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:51.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There's a company called Mandarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There was a competition for \Ncakes using their liquor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.84,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm talking way too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a good listener,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I just get going, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:11.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I really like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,After my shift,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,they said I was relaxed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:21.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It made me wonder what would \Nhave happened if I hadn't been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,After you get used to your job, I'll come visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll give it my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:32.18,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,When I visit, I'll buy a bunch of cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.08,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:49.89,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.91,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,No slacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.20,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.58,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask me anything, if you aren't sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:58.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.97,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ichinose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.49,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You could say I'm the owner's right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.49,SFX-Red,Sign 0505,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20\fad(1,645)}Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:08.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I like baking, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but you're so good, I couldn't help but stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.25,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to become a pâtissier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.67,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.87,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fancy, but you need \Na lot of elbow grease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.50,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0518,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(360,1)}Just wanting it isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.50,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite competitive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.50,SFX-GrayWhite,Sign 0519,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(380,1)}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.13,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose I was in competitions and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.45,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.10,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Good job today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.74,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so I was watching you work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.11,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I think the way you say, "Welcome," is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:47.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.27,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you're too slow at packing cakes in boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Welco—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wel—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:53.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.20,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.62,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't want our store's reputation to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.65,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,The owner told me to teach \Nyou stuff, so that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.63,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, good luck with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Yamato's gotten used to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's better than on her first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:19.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Working for pay is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get much faster at packing cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really like being near cakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and watching people make cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had you come buy any yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,By then, I'll have the job down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:52.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:56.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, considering how she went after you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:06:59.97,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:00.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:03.19,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let what Ichinose-san said get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:03.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.70,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,The way you say, "Welcome," isn't odd at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.81,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose-san doesn't really listen to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.82,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of in his own world, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.34,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly has skills, and he's handsome, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:15.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,His technique is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:21.25,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't take anything he says to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.97,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.21,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:32.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a new product?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So sparkly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it tastes like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.07,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:52.66,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what am I tasting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Bergamot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.15,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet, but slightly sour. Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,An idea a pro would think up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.55,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0810,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(481,644)}Thank you for letting me have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When will we start selling these?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.10,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,We won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:12.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.05,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's a cake I came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:21.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We can't sell your cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.56,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,The owner said it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:29.90,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Once, I sold a cake of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.90,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't sell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:37.66,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand seeing any of my cakes unsold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:46.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about I buy any that are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:49.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can buy up to three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll eat them with my b—those I care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.76,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean the cake's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate it not to be shared with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.77,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0902,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Wonderful \NSo Wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.09,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.41,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,So wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.15,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll have them put three for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to sell them tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.86,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:11.53,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0909,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to sell them! \NFor Ichinose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.53,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,For Ichinose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:17.00,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:20.53,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0918,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to tomorrow. \NI'm looking forward to seeing you, Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:20.01,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to seeing you, Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.21,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0925,0000,0000,0000,,Bergamot Citron
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.21,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look, a new cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.16,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.60,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it tastes like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I highly recommend that cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.85,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll get this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:33.84,Default,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.34,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0936,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(467,1)}This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:38.04,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,I think this girl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.39,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0935,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(488,730)}has feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.55,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0940,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)}for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:42.39,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,has feelings for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.39,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0941,0000,0000,0000,,for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.87,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:48.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.90,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0950,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose-san, your cakes sold out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.90,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,No, I meant your first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, you're even more conspicuous that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want Yamato to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:00.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.08,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.88,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:12.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.80,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.42,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's break time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.20,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1019,0000,0000,0000,,"Rinko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.55,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,"Rinko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.67,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did he call her "Rinko"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:32.98,EyecatchA,Sign 1032,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H887AE6&}Rin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.52,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He was handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, want to get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:45.12,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1044,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}It's only spring, \Nbut from the tan, \Nyou look like a \N"Reverse" game piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.12,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt more than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why not use her first name, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it make you nervous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think Yamato-san would be happy \Nif you used her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:02.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It just doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait, isn't this different?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.79,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It just isn't for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.18,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't easy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:13.85,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's hard for me isn't so hard for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.01,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.45,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.99,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,It was Ichinose-kun's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.25,SFX-BrownWhite,Sign 1128,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(355,1)}Huh? Ichinose-san's idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.25,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You can have any you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.18,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nice and cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.45,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:34.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold and tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:37.46,Default - italics,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose-san smiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.21,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1138,0000,0000,0000,,Shisuda Park Bus Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:41.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:47.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, one of the pâtissiers threw a gelato party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:50.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was him, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:53.48,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.23,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1155,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}What a fancy car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Only geniuses become pâtissiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:56.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,A cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,A fancy car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:59.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I respect him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,A pâtissier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:03.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Professional pâtissiers know so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.62,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What happened between then and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really love my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, I brought you the best-tasting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Have some, too, Sunakawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:23.63,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have told \Nher to get a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.73,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't talk cakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't make them for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is the gelato still okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.89,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1231,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}My hands are cold from holding \Nthem for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:35.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted you to have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.08,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so narrow-minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.61,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Look how happy Yamato is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:48.62,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1245,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(239,1)}Oh, that feels warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not confident in myself as a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.07,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be totally happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.62,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:12:59.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad, Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck at your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:08.10,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought Ichinose-san \Nwould suggest anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.47,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing him talk with Yamato-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.98,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to think he might be nice, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.40,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time we saw him smile, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.57,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose-san's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.92,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.36,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 1322,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(942,1)}Is this fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.36,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Is this fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:26.11,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Is she my muse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.11,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 1324,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(943,1)}Is she my muse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:29.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,carry the small man I am, out to open sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of get what you mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:41.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel this way because of anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of my inability to use her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:49.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm getting hurt because I can't \Neven overcome that little obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a small man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:52.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:57.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's normal to not feel too good about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,seeing guys around your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're just a guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.74,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I never really thought about how
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.96,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato might fall for someone other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:21.63,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,There might be someone she \Ngets along with more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just never thought about that possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.51,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.24,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,because she was always with me, smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.47,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to feel so down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:38.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's only known that guy for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,People don't fall for each other right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:42.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love Yamato, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:46.68,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought everyone \Nwould fall for her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:49.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:51.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your goal for now should \Nbe to use her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.38,Phone,Sign 1459,0000,0000,0000,,Message Inbox \N\NYamato Rinko \NSubject: On Break Right Now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.84,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I got used to my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.38,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so you can come to buy cakes anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:04.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:08.07,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's gelato was a huge hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:09.13,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1508,0000,0000,0000,,Jelly, huh? Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.13,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,What motivated you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:17.22,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about how to make \Nthe person eating it happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.51,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.78,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:25.15,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1521,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.21,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,You have good skills and taste,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:25.15,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,but you've been kind of a lone \Nwolf until now, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.20,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, you've become friendly with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.08,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.03,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.91,SFX-WhiteBlack,Sign 1531,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Pâtissier Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.91,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,If you rank, it'd be great for our store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.03,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd be good for your career, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.35,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,You've been on a roll lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.54,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 1538,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.54,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.54,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1540,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}You'll sign up, right? \NI'll leave this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:39.86,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,you crack me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.76,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,They know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Which cakes would you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm just nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The shortcake is our bestseller.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one shortcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I recommend this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one of that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How many are you going to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:11.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato's working really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:12.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.43,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Were those people just now your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The taller one is my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:30.51,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:31.76,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.26,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Break up with Rinko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.56,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a better fit for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.25,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.98,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1641,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(692,1)}So he does like Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:42.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.31,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to come at you like that, out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.19,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to become a pâtissier, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A pâtissier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.92,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you really like baking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've made cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.82,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Cookies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:00.41,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.45,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Drop cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.02,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Icebox cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:02.50,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Sables?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.25,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rice crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.00,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rice crackers aren't cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.13,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 1707,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a better fit for Rinko for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.13,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a better fit for Rinko for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.29,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two even dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:14.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yamato was getting harassed \Nby a groper, so I helped her—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.38,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 1715,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:15.38,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.58,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,After you helped Rinko out of a tough spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.84,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,she must have seen you as a \Nwonderful, responsible guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:21.10,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.14,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.77,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,She just doesn't know there are other \Nmen who are a better fit for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:31.16,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ichinose Kouki, age 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.85,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pâtissier at Les Cerises.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:36.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gouda Takeo, a first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.03,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 1737,0000,0000,0000,,A first-year in high school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.51,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,A first-year in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.77,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You must have someone who'd be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:44.17,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who's more wild, like a gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.94,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,A bear would work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.04,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you'd have better conversations
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.75,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,if you dated a woman like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.05,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even share the same hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Better conversations...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.05,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Same hobbies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.60,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I need Rinko,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.51,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,so please break up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.53,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.65,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be convinced by what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.87,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I was abrupt, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:16.49,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,But if Rinko asked you, you'd break \Nup with her, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:21.62,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you and Rinko who's the better fit for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.74,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:30.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You could've talked back to him more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:35.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't help but think \Nhe might have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:43.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I can't really talk to \Nher about that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And that there may be others who'd be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.85,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:48.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:49.77,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.50,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.41,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Les Cerises! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.26,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:54.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san's working there part-time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.97,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's perfect for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.28,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,working in a cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.28,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1902,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}I'm not a huge fan of sweets, \Nbut I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised how even Takeo has \Nissues with feeling inferior...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.54,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.54,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1908,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too close, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.00,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that means he \Nhas an inferiority complex,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.17,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,but that is a bit worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:19.68,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, Takeo can put \Nhimself on the back burner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.81,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when he found a lost dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.72,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He became so fond of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.72,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,And he stayed with it for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:34.32,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment he realized the \Ndog might belong to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.19,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1936,0000,0000,0000,,This dog has a collar, so it belonged to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.19,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,he started frantically looking for its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.93,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,When he finally found the owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.53,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo held it together and didn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.59,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was happy for the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.80,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.66,Default,Yuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.85,Default,Yuriko,0000,0000,0000,,The weather forecast was totally off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.32,Default,Yuriko,0000,0000,0000,,It was sunny till just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:56.14,Default,Yuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad didn't take an umbrella with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.33,Default,Yuriko,0000,0000,0000,,No one took an umbrella today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.73,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,What a downpour...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait till the rain dies down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.56,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.60,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver, Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:16.74,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Just to the station, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.90,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my sister just said she'll \Nbring me an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.95,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.66,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Good job today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.81,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:31.04,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.42,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask you, Rinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.81,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to enter a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.17,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think up at least \Nthree original cake recipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.67,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko, would you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:48.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.82,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,With your help, I think I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:54.60,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:57.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:58.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If I can help, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:20.46,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo sometimes puts other people's \Nfeelings before his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:25.47,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,because he just wants the \Nother person to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.36,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,That's both his strength
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.28,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,and his weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:51.01,Title2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,515)}My Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:49.41,Default - margin,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: My Heart.
